quran[6{c,v,t}:
7,82,"magar is ki qoum ka jawab is ke siwa kuch nah tha ke"" nikalu inn logon ko apni bustiyon se, barray pakbaaz bantay hain yeh """
7,83,aakhir-kaar hum ne loot aur iss ke ghar walon ko bajuz is ki biwi ke jo peechay reh jaane walon mein thi
7,84,"bacha kar nikaal diya aur is qoum par brsayi aik barish, phir dekho ke unn mujrimon ka kya injaam howa"
7,85,"aur Mudin walon ki taraf hum ne un ke bhai Shoiab ko bheja is ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, Allah ki bandagi karo, uss ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai tumahray paas tumahray rab ki saaf rahnumai aa gayi hai, lehaza wazan aur pemanay poooray karo, logon ko unn ki cheezon mein ghata nah do, aur zameen mein fasaad barpaa nah karo jab ke is ki islaah ho chuki hai, isi mein tumhari bhalai hai agar tum waqai momin ho"
7,86,"aur ( zindagi ke ) har rastay par rehzan ban kar nah baith jao ke logon ko khauf zada karne aur imaan laane walon ko khuda ke rastay se roknay lagu aur seedhi raah ko terha karne ke darpay ho jao yaad karo woh zamana jabkay tum thoray thay phir Allah ne tumhe bohat kar diya, aur ankhen khol kar dekho ke duniya mein mfsdon ka kya injaam howa hai"
7,87,"agar tum mein se aik giroh is taleem par jis ke sath mein bheja gaya hon, imaan lata hai aur dosra imaan nahi lata, to sabr ke sath dekhte raho yahan taq ke Allah hamaray darmain faisla kar day, aur wohi sab se behtar faisla karne wala hai """
